name: Fresh
description:
A wearable layer to protect your baby from allergens and germs found on clothing while protecting you from spit up, drool, and vomit.

Product Features:

•	100% soft organic cotton
•	One size fits all
•	Wearable barrier that stays in place
•	Elastic neckline to easily put on and take off
•	Exclusive organic prints  
•	Extra layer for multiple usage
•	Large coconut button for easy attachment

BabiLayers is perfect for moms, dads, caregivers, and guests.
Keep your baby healthy and safe this season.
